1243	==== Members
1244	
1245	* [[jjdgm_seed]]
1246	//axl_voices axr_member axd_required
1247	{jjdgm_seed}
1248	is the next
1249	{jjdt_firemark}
1250	to allocate, stored as 2 base64 characters.
1251	Incremented by
1252	{jjdo_create}.
1253	
1254	* [[jjdgm_order]]
1255	//axl_voices axr_member axd_required axd_repeated
1256	{jjdgm_order}
1257	is the ordered list of
1258	{jjdt_firemark_s}
1259	defining heat display and selection order.
1260	Populated from sorted
1261	{jjdgm_heats}
1262	keys on first load of old-format files (migration);
1263	thereafter maintained explicitly.
1264	Updated by:
1265	{jjdo_create}
1266	(append new firemark),
1267	{jjdo_archive}
1268	(remove firemark via retain),
1269	{jjdo_continue}
1270	(move new firemark to position 0).
1271	{jjdgm_order}
1272	is the authoritative source for display and selection order, not
1273	{jjdgm_heats}
1274	key order.
1275	
1276	* [[jjdgm_version]]
1277	//axl_voices axr_member axd_optional axt_number
1278	{jjdgm_version}
1279	is the schema version number.
